# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# OPSCORD — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and fill in your values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Database (Supabase) ─────────────────
# Pooled connection (port 6543) — used by the app at runtime
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres.[PROJECT_REF]:Dharhara4247@@aws-1-ap-southeast-2.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true"
# Direct connection (port 5432) — used for Prisma migrations only
DIRECT_URL="postgresql://postgres.[PROJECT_REF]:Dharhara4247@@aws-1-ap-southeast-2.pooler.supabase.com:5432/postgres"

# ── Redis (Upstash) ────────────────────
REDIS_URL="redis://localhost:6379"
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=""
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=""

# ── Auth (Clerk) ───────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=""
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=""
CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET=""

# ── AI (OpenRouter + Gemini) ───────────
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=""
GEMINI_API_KEY=""

# ── Observability (Sentry) ─────────────
SENTRY_DSN=""
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=""
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=""                  # For source maps upload

# ── Analytics (PostHog) ────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=""
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST="https://us.i.posthog.com"

# ── Services ───────────────────────────
API_PORT=4000
INGESTION_PORT=4001
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL="http://localhost:4000"
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL="ws://localhost:4000"

# ── Logging ────────────────────────────
LOG_LEVEL="debug"
